metadata.name: Flourish
metadata.description:
My girl!
You are like a flower,
flourishing through the darkest days...

You are the whole nature,
The seed of your love paints the world in beautiful colors

.. 

I know about the stormy days,
I know about the tears,

I don't want you to forget
I want you to remember 
To remember Yourself!


----
4000 * 5700 pixels
